{"tid":1244723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1989年北京學生如何以非暴力突破軍警封鎖","createTime":"2019-06-20T04:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T06:27:35.000Z","uid":36901,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd20d6281e1575c73e9cf2960f512385996900d4","tid":1244723,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"1989年4月26日人民日報將北京學潮定性為動亂，引起全民擔心對學生秋後算帳<br />\n<br />\n第二日，4月27日，北京學生不理中共禁令<br />\n發起大遊行直操天安門廣場<br />\n可能好多新一代完全未聽過<br />\n但呢次遊行對整場學運影響深遠<br />\n北京學生沒有雞蛋，沒有大衝突，甚至沒有辱罵<br />\n單純手翹手唱歌，用非暴力突破軍警重重封鎖<br />\n成為以後非暴力抗爭典範<br />\n<br />\n呢件事，令北京學生獲得急速支持<br />\n5月香港更有150萬香港人支持學運<br />\n係616前香港最多人示威記錄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OHA7F-v_4K8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOHA7F-v_4K8&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=0822997a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OHA7F-v_4K8</a>"},{"pid":"22fb5c3d1e908623a90e10241a05db8d45dae558","tid":1244723,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7556a4d55d17dc89e09bacb1b2b47ce062ce2794","tid":1244723,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"無大台無組織無指揮官 就做唔到有系統研究戰術"},{"pid":"8a17b2e1b2ea9c6d46b8a1b66947a23692e80cd1","tid":1244723,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7556a4d55d17dc89e09bacb1b2b47ce062ce2794","tid":1244723,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"無大台無組織無指揮官 就做唔到有系統研究戰術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"其實當年427遊行指揮組織力<br />\n我覺得還不及現在香港學生<br />\n呢類非暴力抗爭<br />\n反而係好靠群眾自覺性<br />\n目標清晰<br />\n大家都知道民心界限係邊"},{"pid":"4bb796e48e3baea1831972990761c0a913abfe6b","tid":1244723,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"621 醜事傳千里，輿論救義士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244725</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n新部署，入嚟討論"},{"pid":"424e575f8548537cb7d27b1dc4d13ccde8451d50","tid":1244723,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"宜家仲可唔可以咁做？"},{"pid":"f96a391f76738d12c711276443518bd64bf3ce05","tid":1244723,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"424e575f8548537cb7d27b1dc4d13ccde8451d50","tid":1244723,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"宜家仲可唔可以咁做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"係中國當然完全冇條件<br />\n但香港就還有機,<br />\n非暴力畢竟係最多人能接受到<br />\n<br />\n呢類運動要有幾個條件<br />\n<br />\n1.民心團結<br />\n2.遊行訴求獲得市民同情/支持<br />\n3.政權處於虛怯/不一致狀態"},{"pid":"942b88184d26691d96fcaa5e213f4cf39f3252d0","tid":1244723,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64711d830621940b650227388cc80c82c36fa922","tid":1244723,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"正！請問北京學生最後下場係點？"},{"pid":"93f77de5204d8fcbcda95b4f08e61b26bedc9a50","tid":1244723,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64711d830621940b650227388cc80c82c36fa922","tid":1244723,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"正！請問北京學生最後下場係點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"死撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5eafabb6148f12941f77bd69929f4ade451849","tid":1244723,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"64711d8306